body_full_text:
{{ contact.firstname }},

You've had your system for about three weeks now. By this point, most customers tell us the initial adjustment period is over and the system feels like part of their daily routine.

I'd genuinely like to know how it's going for you.

**A quick favor:** If you're happy with your system, would you mind leaving a short review? It doesn't need to be long — even a sentence or two helps future customers who are in the same position you were a month ago.

[Leave a Review →]

**Looking ahead:**

{% if deal.hsc_quote_base_type == "swiss_lace" %}
Your Swiss Lace system typically lasts 3-4 months. I'd recommend starting to think about your next order around month 3 so there's no gap.
{% elif deal.hsc_quote_base_type == "french_lace" %}
Your French Lace system typically lasts 4-6 months. I'll check in with you around month 4 to see if you're ready for your next one.
{% elif deal.hsc_quote_base_type == "nano_skin" %}
Your Nano Skin system typically lasts 1-2 months. I'll reach out around the 3-4 week mark to see how it's holding up.
{% elif deal.hsc_quote_base_type == "micro_skin" or deal.hsc_quote_base_type == "thin_skin" %}
Your skin base system typically lasts 3-6 months. I'll check in at the halfway point to see if you're ready.
{% elif deal.hsc_quote_base_type == "dura_skin" %}
Your Dura Skin system is built for maximum durability — typically 4-8 months. I'll reach out around month 4.
{% elif deal.hsc_quote_base_type == "mono" %}
Your Mono Pro system typically lasts 5-8 months. I'll reach out around month 5.
{% else %}
Based on your base type, I'll reach out when you're likely approaching replacement time to make your reorder seamless.
{% endif %}

When that time comes, your second order will be faster — we already have your spec on file and can make adjustments if anything needs tweaking (color, density, base fit).

Vincent
Hair Solutions Co.

{{ contact.firstname }},

I'd like to make it easy for you to come back.

**Here's a returning-customer offer:** $[X] off your next system order.

This applies to your exact spec on file:
{% if contact.hsc_last_known_system_family %}
- System: {{ contact.hsc_last_known_system_family }}
{% endif %}
{% if contact.hsc_density_preference %}
- Density: {{ contact.hsc_density_preference }}%
{% endif %}

If you want to adjust anything — base type, density, color — that's fine too. The offer applies regardless.

**To redeem:**
Reply "I'm ready" and I'll send a quote with the discount applied. Or if you need to adjust your spec first, reply with what you'd like to change.

This offer is valid for 14 days.

Vincent
Hair Solutions Co.
